CONSUMED-ONLY SOURCES  (cited/linked, NOT redistributed)
--------------------------------------------------------

The following inform analysis and may be cited, but their raw content and any
derived scores are NOT bundled, exported, or served by SkillCurrent:

    - AIOE (Felten, Raj & Seamans) — citation-only, redistribution-restricted.
    - GDPval-AA (Artificial Analysis Elo) — not openly licensed.
    - OpenAI GDPval leaderboard scores — view-only. SkillCurrent instead
      regenerates its own scores via the public grader on the MIT task set.
    - SML (Brynjolfsson et al.) and Webb (2020) — academic / citation-only.


